videos.headline: Hailey Van Lith sinks the 3-pointer for the Cardinals
videos.description: The Louisville Cardinals share the rock and eventually find Hailey Van Lith, who hits the trey.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Hailey Van Lith sinks the 3-pointer for the Cardinals) 2023/03/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hailey Van Lith hits the smooth trey
videos.description: Hailey Van Lith causally motions into her shot and knocks down the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Hailey Van Lith hits the smooth trey) 2023/03/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Myah Taylor buries the nice 3-pointer
videos.description: Myah Taylor is poised on offense as she steps into her shot and nails the trey.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Myah Taylor buries the nice 3-pointer) 2023/03/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hailey Van Lith drops in the corner 3
videos.description: Mykasa Robinson keeps her eyes on the defense and finds Hailey Van Lith for a nice jumper.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Hailey Van Lith drops in the corner 3) 2023/03/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mykasa Robinson drops off a sweet dime for 2
videos.description: Mykasa Robinson finds a cutting Hailey Van Lith, who hits the easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Check out this sweet pass from Mykasa Robinson) 2023/03/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Madison Scott gets and-1 layup to go
videos.description: Madison Scott pushes the ball down the floor, then she switches directions to get the layup plus a foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Madison Scott gets and-1 layup to go) 2023/03/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Olivia Cochran hits the strong and-1 layup
videos.description: Olivia Cochran makes a tough move, then finishes inside with a tough and-1 layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Olivia Cochran hits the strong and-1 layup) 2023/03/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Magical run of Ole Miss ends with loss at Louisville
videos.description: The 8-seed Rebels put up a tremendous fight before falling on the road to the 5-seed Cardinals, ending their Cinderella season in the NCAA Tournament.
